 decca ➡   912586 ➡ 4
  fade ➡    64222 ➡ 7
  face ➡    64206 ➡ 9
  deaf ➡    57007 ➡ 1
  cafe ➡    51966 ➡ 9
  bead ➡    48813 ➡ 6
